        <ontology:took_place_at rdf:resource="https://dlnarratives.eu/phenomenal_place/40.37778036234481_-7.71916572654535"/>
        <ontology:hasDescription>Will climate change affect strawberry trees distribution and Strawberry tree fruit quality?. Overall the type of challenge faced by this VC is Predicted. This VC is classified as Traditional.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


